sourcesContent: import React from 'react' import { ServiceCardContainer, InfoWrapper, InfoRow, Column1, Column2, ImgWrap, Img, TextWrapper, TopLine, Subtitle} from '../ServiceElements' const Card = ({ id, imgStart, topLine, description1, description2,description3, img, alt}) => { return ( <> {topLine} {description1} {description2} {description3} ) } export default Card
